title: Race of Champions 2012 - Nations Cup ROC
description:
Race of Champions Live 2012 - Day 1 - Nations Cup Full coverage of day one from this years RoC - It's the Nations Cup! Aired on Saturday 15th of December 2012 The likes of Sebastien Vettel, Michael Schumacher and David Coulthard come together to battle for national pride in a variety of machinery as part of this season-ending extravaganza.
